Barry Lyttle pleaded guilty to recklessly causing grievous bodily harm to his brother Patrick in January . 
  Patrick Lyttle was left in a coma after he was allegedly struck by his brother in Kings Cross in Sydney . 
  Barry Lyttle will now be sentenced in Sydney's local court rather than the district court . 
  The Irish tourist has called on charges against his brother to be dropped . 
  Patrick spent six days in an induced coma following the attack . 
 